<!-- About Content -->
<div class="container mb-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
      <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
      <p>TypeScribr was founded in 2023 with a simple mission: to create a platform that connects talented writers with quality writing opportunities while ensuring fair compensation for their work.</p>
      <p>We recognized that many freelance writers struggle to find consistent, well-paying work, while businesses and publishers often have difficulty finding reliable, skilled writers. TypeScribr bridges this gap by providing a curated platform where writers can access pre-vetted assignments.</p>
      <p>Our team consists of experienced writers, editors, and tech professionals who understand the challenges of the writing industry and are committed to creating a better ecosystem for all stakeholders.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400?text=Our+Team" alt="Our Team" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
      <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>At TypeScribr, our mission is to empower writers by providing them with a reliable platform to showcase their skills, access quality assignments, and earn fair compensation for their work.</p>
      <p>We believe that good writing deserves recognition and fair payment. By creating a transparent and supportive environment, we aim to elevate the standard of content creation while ensuring writers receive the compensation they deserve.</p>
      <p>We are committed to continuous improvement and growth, constantly seeking feedback from our community to enhance the platform and provide better opportunities for all our users.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400?text=Our+Mission" alt="Our Mission" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
    </div>
  </div>
